}},"testimonials_hhQqdV":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_MzXpmt":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>\"Mujhe honestly expect nahi tha ke online toy itna acha hoga, lekin Toylicious ne surprise kar diya. Quality bhi achi thi aur delivery bhi time pe hogayi. Mere bhatijay ko bohat pasand aaya!\"<br\/><br\/><\/p>","author":"Fatima Siddiqui","author_info":""}},"testimonial_gyneXc":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p><br\/>\"Excellent collection aur reasonable prices. Mera beta bohat khush hua apna favorite action figure dekh kar!\"<br\/><br\/><\/p>","author":"Ayesha Khan","author_info":""}},"testimonial_7Gtr4U":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p><strong>\"میری بیٹی کو گڑیا کے کھلونے بہت پسند ہیں، اور جب اسے ٹوئی لیشس سے نیا ڈول ہاؤس ملا تو وہ بہت خوش ہوئی۔ چیز بہت خوبصورت اور محفوظ طریقے سے پیک کی گئی تھی۔ شاپنگ کا تجربہ واقعی بہترین رہا\"<\/strong><\/p>","author":"فرح ناز","author_info":""}},"testimonial_YXr3Rr":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>\"Pehli baar order diya tha thoda doubt tha, lekin jab toy mila toh sab clear hogaya. Bilkul waisa hi tha jaisa dikhaya gaya tha. Customer support ne bhi help ki jab tracking mein confusion hua.\"<br\/><br\/><\/p>","author":"Mariam Javed","author_info":""}},"testimonial_r7idyP":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>\"Mujhe yeh pasand aya ke yeh log sirf fancy toys nahi, balkay quality aur safe toys bhi dete hain. Mera chhota bhai roz usi se khelta hai ab. Trust bana hai Toylicious pe.\"<br\/><br\/><\/p>","author":"Hamza Tariq","author_info":""}},"testimonial_zUUF3K":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>\"My daughter is obsessed with the dollhouse we bought! Thank you, Toylicious.\"<\/p>","author":"Zara Javed","author_info":""}},"testimonial_fChgQ9":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"icon":"5-stars","testimonial":"<p>\"S